Package: libqoriq-rcw0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: QorIQ Reset Configuration Word compiler library (runtime)
 libqoriq-rcw is a C library for compiling NXP QorIQ Reset Configuration
 Word source files into PBL/RCW binary images, and for decompiling those
 images back to source text. It targets the PBI format 2 platforms:
 LS1028, LS1088, LS2088 and LX2160 SoC families.
 .
 This package contains the shared library used at runtime.

Package: libqoriq-rcw-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 libqoriq-rcw0 (= ${binary:Version}),
 libmcpp-dev,
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: QorIQ Reset Configuration Word compiler library (development files)
 libqoriq-rcw is a C library for compiling NXP QorIQ Reset Configuration
 Word source files into PBL/RCW binary images, and for decompiling those
 images back to source text. It targets the PBI format 2 platforms:
 LS1028, LS1088, LS2088 and LX2160 SoC families.
 .
 This package contains the C header, static library, pkg-config file and
 man page needed to build software against libqoriq-rcw.
